{"id":"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration","title":"provideClientHydration","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\", \"name\": \"provideClientHydration\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts#L99-L174\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"provideclienthydration\">provideClientHydration<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#provideclienthydration\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9ocozh78o7mc6fu2dr7uure0v\">设置必要的提供者，以启用应用程序的水合功能。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideClientHydration</a></span>(...features: <a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"38fwf35xy1ajri4niursk05yy\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>features</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeatureKind</a>&gt;[]</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"67itsaydzdea5mq46miulsd2y\">配置其他路由器行为的可选特性。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">返回值</h6>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bp4dhrfep9ace17adjs124jmw\">一组启用水合的提供程序。</p>\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoHttpTransferCache\"><code>withNoHttpTransferCache</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withHttpTransferCacheOptions\"><code>withHttpTransferCacheOptions</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6av2o2cp9k8gn76suahj8asg5\">默认情况下，该函数会启用推荐的一组特性，以实现大多数应用程序的最佳性能。它包括以下特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a5gui5cs56kelu5rbj5i68z7f\">协调 DOM 水合。在这里了解更多信息\n<a href=\"guide/hydration\">。</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4pi7iy6iw54u9vx2n0tq8suow\"><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\"><code>HttpClient</code></a> 在服务器上运行时的响应缓存，并将此缓存传输到客户端，以避免额外的 HTTP 请求。在这里了解更多关于数据缓存的信息\n<a href=\"/guide/ssr#caching-data-when-using-httpclient\">。</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f20098j34d8c48uns1ynsvuw4\">这些函数允许你禁用一些默认特性或配置特性</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4il2mnwwcgzv45cggserg1q3u\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoHttpTransferCache\"><code>withNoHttpTransferCache</code></a> 用于禁用 HTTP 传输缓存</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"17bus8doz1vvnhx4apvvphr3v\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withHttpTransferCacheOptions\"><code>withHttpTransferCacheOptions</code></a> 用于配置一些 HTTP 传输缓存选项</li>\n</ul>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8wvb98i9b5gqwuydq630v7whn\">更多信息请参见\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1wtq4ellw1swfwpcehm758phd\">使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 函数时如何在应用程序中启用水合的基本示例：</p>\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(AppComponent, {\n  providers: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideClientHydration</a>()]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cs4btw864uztl4xkn01dhvt9q\">或者，如果你使用的是 NgModules，你可以将 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideClientHydration</a></code> 添加到根应用程序模块的提供者列表中。</p>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  declarations: [RootCmp],\n  bootstrap: [RootCmp],\n  providers: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideClientHydration</a>()],\n})\nexport class AppModule {}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser\n - errors/NG0505\n - guide/hydration\n - guide/ssr\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - /guide/ssr#caching-data-when-using-httpclient\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - api/core/EnvironmentProviders\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\n - api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#description\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#provideclienthydration\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#see-also\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/withHttpTransferCacheOptions\n - api/platform-browser/withNoHttpTransferCache\n - guide/hydration\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts#L99-L174\n-->"}